{"tid":713044,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港旗生日蛋糕","createTime":"2018-06-22T14:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T03:03:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"587dd177a3376be116d78dd7db945494a467e53a","tid":713044,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180622/20427360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427360&d=ehzDsiRqX84m4WCA67yTep7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3a9cea3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427360&h=2f39a1fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180622/20427360</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港旗生日蛋糕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180622/large/e8809a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180622%2Flarge%2Fe8809a.jpg&h=37bb3f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高慧然facebook圖片<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n約了幾個好友去九州旅行，正好撞正朋友生日，順便幫朋友慶祝生日。<br />\n<br />\n入住嬉野的那一天，朋友的生日已經過去了，吃完一泊二食溫泉酒店的晚餐，包房的燈突然熄滅了，我們正在納悶，門外突然響起音樂聲，侍應唱着生日歌推門而入，手上捧着燃燒的煙火和甜品。<br />\n<br />\n朋友的眼神在我們幾個人身上輪流掃視一遍，想知道是誰安排的驚喜，因為過去兩天，我們三個人分別為她準備了兩次生日驚喜。但是這一次，送上生日驚喜的，原來是溫泉酒店！相信是訂房時他們留意到了客人的出生日期，即使生日已經過去一天，仍細心送上甜品和祝福。<br />\n<br />\n比這個更令人驚喜和感動的，是壽星婆的甜品上插着一支香港區旗！酒店出手舒爽，不但壽星婆有甜品吃，其他三位客人也有。四個人四份甜品，兩份插香港區旗，兩份插日本國旗。我們確實被深深地打動了，望着這兩面旗，眼角有一點點濕。<br />\n<br />\n日本人清楚知道，香港人和中國人是不一樣的，香港是一個與中國不一樣的地方。在香港這個城巿漸漸被融入大灣區的今天，九州溫泉鄉，一間溫泉酒店對香港人身份的認同和肯定，着實令人鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n我們離開餐廳的時候，料理長親自來到門口向我們鞠躬，並一直站在門外送我們。我有點後悔沒有邀請料理長和我們合影留念。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=ehzDsiRqX84m4WCA67yTep7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9b313326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n詞　語 (林道群)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n那得不倒楣 (古德明)"},{"pid":"97e3dd7d48866a9b75f8a6f2900a3ed967081ea9","tid":713044,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:05:59.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩，抽氣扇有咩好"},{"pid":"76d339012918ecacb777374644d7cf7b00fa1bb9","tid":713044,"uid":59669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/221503_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F221503_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e89f9d63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5344d4b633efd38b104ca93886be0a09142410c7","tid":713044,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d339012918ecacb777374644d7cf7b00fa1bb9","tid":713044,"uid":59669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/221503_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F221503_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e89f9d63&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔撚想要支共啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"4484eb351f1bdce5054e82bbfd65fade1553dc7e","tid":713044,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d339012918ecacb777374644d7cf7b00fa1bb9","tid":713044,"uid":59669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:15: